Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: detroit bar hop
des: Just ask Detroit Bar Hop to find a bar and it will search for all currently open bars/lounges that are in Downtown Detroit. It will also provide you with the rating, number of reviews, address, and a scope of price!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
